  "texts": [
    "Since an asynchronous MARL approach is used, agents are not active during every step.",
    "A mask is used to mark only the active steps of the agent and use only these steps for updating the policy.",
    "Initial experiments on various sized datasets indicated a very high variance regarding the reward function.",
    "To reduce the variance, one scenario is used for decoder training and parameter optimization.",
    "A low variance is beneficial for the training process, since then changes in the reward function only relate to the agent's behavior."
  ],
